						"title": "Secure your APIs with Cloudflare API Gateway",
						"subtitle": null,
						"copy": "The rise of APIs has presented exciting business opportunities to deliver products faster and improve customer experience. However, APIs also carry sensitive data, making them very attractive to attackers. Data breaches and leaks through APIs have made headlines in recent years, putting customer trust at risk. Modern CISOs and security leaders are tasked with balancing innovation with securing their APIs. With Cloudflare API Gateway, you can protect your organization's sensitive data and keep customer trust intact.\n\nSign up now to learn how we can help your organization:\n\n- Protect public APIs without disrupting innovation\n- Secure your business growth with a programmatic approach to API security\n- Gain no-hassle visibility into all your public APIs, schemas, and usage\n- Consolidate your application security program with Cloudflare's Application Security platform\n\nFor strategies on securing your APIs, [download the CISO's Guide to API Security below](#guide).",
